{"tid":1527040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係名古屋飛緊番香港8pm到 如期抵港","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:23:52.000Z","uid":146499,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce12c3538017094f5fb10096b84e046ca30bed0","tid":1527040,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"我坐  CX539 8pm 抵港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成機幾百個旅客</span> delay40mins 但機長話加快航程如期到達<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲係大把機飛緊去香港，popo撚夠膽係機場開拖？</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">係冇可能架！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">散水撚收皮啦</span>"},{"pid":"1c16a6e616e17e538be946b0de6210aab8ab14c1","tid":1527040,"uid":146499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"機場Group有大量散水撚，要睇機場資訊就睇機場Channel(呂麗乳搖巴）。謹記：<br />\n- 好多手足從各方入緊機場（巴士/東涌冒雨行）<br />\n- 機場運作正常，有好多旅客<br />\n- 人越多就越安全<br />\n- 散防散水撚（記唔記得上次佔機場發生過咩？就係乜事都無！但散水嘅風卻係所有運動之中最高）<br />\n- 諗下琴晚各區發生過乜？點可以走得落？<br />\n- 機場比起市區更安全，因為有旅客同埋國際形象要顧<br />\n<br />\n萬事小人，好多手足入緊嚟，到時見❤️"},{"pid":"c9777b8a71719e860019a2cb4f57ccb223bc24cb","tid":1527040,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkvjRm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkvjRm4.png&h=be721d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足聽日罷課罷工返課返工都好，可唔可以應承我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304b48d370605deb691ea84c2073158acaca1666","tid":1527040,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hLcrWH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hLcrWH.jpg&h=3451768e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88b3b1ef6979afd977e3202b5f222f1243338de7","tid":1527040,"uid":263